parameters:
\nc<>I came here with Reina to destroy the seeds... and then...
ugh!
\nc<>(My head hurts... I can't remember clearly... but first--)
\nc<？？？>Kei-chan, are you okay? Are you hurt anywhere?

\ncYeah, it's me, Hina. What's wrong? You look like you've seen
a ghost or something.

\nc<>(No way... Hina-chan and I had a huge fight in middle
school and stopped talking to each other...)

\nc<>(No, wait, weren't you much younger back then?)
(Elementary school?)

\ncKei-chan, you're such a weirdo. Did you leave your homework
at school? Hurry up and go get it so we can play!
\nc<>(I... I remembered. It must be that day.)

\nc<>The day I went to school to get my homework and encountered
a villain, becoming a magical girl.
\nc<>The day my life took a turn for the worse.

\nc<>(Look, when we enter the premises, we can hear the sound of
the villain causing a commotion...!)

\ncWell, of course, right? If you tell the security guard at
our school, you can come and go normally.
\nc<>The villain!? They were on the news yesterday, right?

\ncVil...lain...? The bad person? I don't think they've been in
the recent news...

\nc<>The enemy of the magical girl who occasionally jumps out
from another world and causes harm!

\nc...Kei-chan, have you watched anime? I also like anime, you
know.

\ncEven though we'll be in middle school the year after next,
those kind of detailed settings are a bit risky...
\nc<Hina>Well, because it's no good if I'm not by your side.
\nc<>Sorry, there's a place I want to stop by for a bit!
